Sentencas: This study describes the development of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) stack with external manifold structure.
Titulo: Performance degradation and analysis of 10-cell anode-supported SOFC stack with external manifold structure

Sentencas: The stack used anode supported cells with size of 11 cm x 11 cm which are fabricated by tape casting, screen-printing and co-sintering.
Titulo: Performance degradation and analysis of 10-cell anode-supported SOFC stack with external manifold structure

Sentencas: Computer simulation was employed to evaluate the gas distribution in the external manifold stack.
Titulo: Performance degradation and analysis of 10-cell anode-supported SOFC stack with external manifold structure

Sentencas: The 10-cell stack was operated at 750 C-omicron with hydrogen as fuel and air as oxidant and generated output power of 360 W, corresponding to power density of 440 mW/cm(2).
Titulo: Performance degradation and analysis of 10-cell anode-supported SOFC stack with external manifold structure

Sentencas: The degradation performance was investigated for over 750 h under the current density of 370 mA/cm(2).
Titulo: Performance degradation and analysis of 10-cell anode-supported SOFC stack with external manifold structure

Sentencas: Posttest analysis of the SOFC stack was operated to investigate the factors related to the performance degradation such as microstructure of electrodes, sealing, contact resistance and oxidation of metal interconnect.
Titulo: Performance degradation and analysis of 10-cell anode-supported SOFC stack with external manifold structure

Sentencas: The study presented here showed the stack with external manifold can be considered as a strong candidate for SOFC stack design.
Titulo: Performance degradation and analysis of 10-cell anode-supported SOFC stack with external manifold structure
